-- Fujifilm May Post First-Quarter Profit on LCD Film, Cost Cuts, Nikkei Says
-- Fergus Maguire
-- 2010-07-12T21:45:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/fujifilm-may-post-first-quarter-profit-on-lcd-film-cost-cuts-nikkei-says.html

          
          
             Fujifilm Holdings Corp. may post
first-quarter operating profit of about 40 billion yen on demand
for protective film used in LCD panels and cost cuts, Nikkei
English News said, without citing anyone. The company reported a
year-earlier loss of 2.7 billion yen.  
 Sales in the April-June period may rise 7 percent to about
540 billion yen, the report said.  
          
          


  


        